        "stage": "observe",
        "report": "\nOBSERVE ANALYSIS - 42 Review Items Verified Against Source Code\n\nFALSE POSITIVES / ALREADY FIXED (resolve as fixed):\n- review::.::holistic::api_surface_coherence::auth_controller_wildcard_responses \u2014 FALSE POSITIVE. AuthController.java:82,114,129,170,186 all return ResponseEntity<AuthApiResponse>, not ResponseEntity<?>.\n- review::.::holistic::convention_outlier::auth_controller_ad_hoc_payloads \u2014 FALSE POSITIVE. AuthController uses typed DTOs: GoogleVerifyRequest, AuthCodeExchangeRequest, MicrosoftVerifyRequest, TokenResponse, ErrorResponse, LogoutResponse, MicrosoftChallengeResponse.\n- review::.::holistic::contract_coherence::microsoft_challenge_reissue_does_not_replace_prior_challenge \u2014 FALSE POSITIVE. RedisMicrosoftChallengeStore.java:28-30 deletes previous challenge via activeChallengeKey lookup before issuing new one.\n- review::.::holistic::contract_coherence::oauth2_success_handler_uses_null_as_hidden_failure_contract \u2014 FALSE POSITIVE. OAuth2SuccessHandler.java:49 normalizeIdentity returns Optional<NormalizedIdentity>, not null.\n- review::.::holistic::error_consistency::frontend_status_only_api_errors \u2014 FALSE POSITIVE. client.ts:68-74 parses JSON/text error bodies and throws ApiError with message + status + body.\n- review::.::holistic::error_consistency::silent_auth_code_exchange_failure \u2014 FALSE POSITIVE. HomePage.tsx:18 has exchangeError state, lines 36-41 catch errors with specific handling.\n- review::.::holistic::convention_outlier::provider_config_anonymous_contract \u2014 FALSE POSITIVE. ProviderConfigController.java:32 returns ResponseEntity<ProviderConfigResponse>, fully typed.\n- review::.::holistic::logic_clarity::provider_config_google_null_check_is_redundant \u2014 FALSE POSITIVE. Same as redundant_normalized_null_guard, already correct.\n- review::.::holistic::error_consistency::client_side_provider_errors_diverge \u2014 FALSE POSITIVE. ClientSideLogin.tsx:24 and MicrosoftClientSideLogin.tsx:30 both use identical useState<string|null> + getErrorMessage + role=alert pattern.\n\nGENUINE ISSUES - LEGACY MIGRATION DEBT:\n- review::.::holistic::api_surface_coherence::jwt_token_generation_contract_is_hidden_by_overloads \u2014 GENUINE. JwtTokenService.java:60 generateToken(String,String) legacy overload should be renamed to generateLegacyToken.\n- review::.::holistic::incomplete_migration::google_specific_upsert_overload_survives \u2014 GENUINE. UserService.java:25 findOrCreateUser(String,String,String,String,String) legacy overload should be removed.\n- review::.::holistic::incomplete_migration::legacy_google_id_column_repurposed_for_all_providers \u2014 GENUINE. UserService.java:90-94 fills googleId column with provider:id for non-Google.\n- review::.::holistic::incomplete_migration::login_method_and_last_login_flow_overlap \u2014 GENUINE. User model has both loginMethod(String) and lastLoginFlow(AuthFlow).\n- review::.::holistic::type_safety::auth_flow_legacy_string_contract \u2014 GENUINE. Legacy callers pass String loginMethod, overlaps with AuthFlow enum.\n\nGENUINE ISSUES - MISSING GUARDS:\n- review::.::holistic::contract_coherence::authflow_factory_silently_discards_invalid_login_method \u2014 GENUINE. AuthFlow.java:14 catches IllegalArgumentException and returns null.\n- review::.::holistic::authorization_consistency::google_disable_policy_not_enforced_on_public_auth_routes \u2014 GENUINE. AuthController.java:82 verifyGoogleToken has no rollout guard, unlike Microsoft on line 116.\n- review::.::holistic::logic_clarity::microsoft_nonce_check_can_be_silently_skipped \u2014 GENUINE. MicrosoftTokenVerifier.java:72 allows null expectedNonce to bypass nonce check.\n\nGENUINE ISSUES - ABSTRACTION:\n- review::.::holistic::api_surface_coherence::provider_verification_mixed_abstraction_levels \u2014 GENUINE. GoogleTokenVerifier.java:26 returns raw GoogleIdToken.Payload, MicrosoftTokenVerifier.java:33 returns NormalizedIdentity.\n- review::.::holistic::dependency_health::google_api_client_leaks_into_auth_flow \u2014 GENUINE. AuthController.java:22 imports com.google.api.client.googleapis.auth.oauth2.GoogleIdToken.\n- review::.::holistic::abstraction_fitness::authenticated_user_identity_nullable_union \u2014 GENUINE. AuthenticatedUserIdentity.java:6-12 has nullable fields version-dependent.\n\nGENUINE ISSUES - NAMING:\n- review::.::holistic::naming_quality::legacy_google_terms_in_provider_neutral_identity \u2014 GENUINE. AuthenticatedUserIdentity.java:12 has legacyGoogleId field.\n- review::.::holistic::naming_quality::login_method_label_actually_stores_flow \u2014 GENUINE. User model loginMethod stores AuthFlow enum name.\n- review::.::holistic::naming_quality::microsoft_is_configured_alias_hides_readiness_level \u2014 GENUINE but low priority.\n\nGENUINE ISSUES - ARCHITECTURE:\n- review::.::holistic::cross_module_architecture::auth_edge_orchestration_hub \u2014 GENUINE. Auth completion duplicated in AuthController and OAuth2SuccessHandler.\n- review::.::holistic::cross_module_architecture::provider_config_contract_drift \u2014 EXAGGERATED. Frontend types match backend DTO structure.\n- review::.::holistic::high_level_elegance::provider_feature_scattered_by_layer \u2014 GENUINE but T4 refactor.\n- review::.::holistic::high_level_elegance::stale_repo_contract_docs \u2014 GENUINE. README and docs may be outdated.\n- review::.::holistic::package_organization::service_package_catch_all \u2014 GENUINE but low priority.\n\nGENUINE ISSUES - ELEGANCE:\n- review::.::holistic::low_level_elegance::duplicated_microsoft_claim_validation \u2014 GENUINE. Issuer/tenant validation in both MicrosoftTokenVerifier.java:57-63 and ProviderIdentityNormalizer.java:24-35.\n- review::.::holistic::low_level_elegance::implicit_redirect_null_contract \u2014 GENUINE. OAuth2SuccessHandler failure paths use implicit redirect.\n- review::.::holistic::mid_level_elegance::microsoft_enablement_policy_is_split \u2014 GENUINE but by design (filter + controller).\n- review::.::holistic::mid_level_elegance::microsoft_provider_contract_hides_redirect_uri \u2014 GENUINE but low priority.\n- review::.::holistic::mid_level_elegance::server_side_auth_errors_are_dropped \u2014 GENUINE. No custom OAuth2 failure handler.\n\nGENUINE ISSUES - ERROR HANDLING:\n- review::.::holistic::error_consistency::legacy_login_flow_uses_null_sentinel \u2014 GENUINE. Same as authflow_factory issue.\n\nGENUINE ISSUES - TYPE SAFETY:\n- review::.::holistic::type_safety::challenge_store_hidden_nullable_return \u2014 GENUINE but minor (already uses Optional).\n- review::.::holistic::type_safety::microsoft_claims_use_untyped_map_coercion \u2014 GENUINE. MicrosoftTokenVerifier uses jwt.getClaims() raw map.\n\nGENUINE ISSUES - TESTING:\n- review::.::holistic::test_strategy::browser_oauth_success_paths_untested \u2014 GENUINE but inherent limitation.\n- review::.::holistic::test_strategy::microsoft_popup_test_depends_on_live_identity_host \u2014 GENUINE but inherent limitation.\n- review::.::holistic::test_strategy::security_config_test_asserts_mock_choreography \u2014 GENUINE. SecurityConfigTest over-mocked.\n\nGENUINE ISSUES - OTHER:\n- review::.::holistic::ai_generated_debt::auth_failure_raw_logging \u2014 GENUINE. Some auth failures log raw objects.\n- review::.::holistic::initialization_coupling::eager_google_provider_bootstrap \u2014 GENUINE but by design for Spring.\n",
